.git
.github
target
# Host node_modules (built for the host OS/pnpm store) must not enter the build
# context: `pnpm install` in the image would otherwise try to purge the stale
# dir and abort with no TTY. The image installs its own fresh copy.
**/node_modules
# Build artifacts (gitignored): the image builds its own from source, so a stale
# host dist (e.g. compiled tests from an older build) must not leak into it.
**/dist
dev/data
.DS_Store
*.log
